Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 3/17/2025

1. Introduction
We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our App, which is designed to display car listings and showrooms for buying and selling cars.

2. Information We Collect
Phone Permission: The App requests access to your phone solely to allow you to directly call car owners.
Internet Access: We use internet connectivity to fetch and display car listings and showroom details from our servers.
User Data: The App does not require you to create an account, provide payment details, or enter any personal information beyond what is necessary for its basic functions.
3. How We Use Your Information
Phone Functionality: The phone permission is used exclusively to initiate calls to car owners.
Displaying Information: Internet access is used to retrieve and display current car listings and showroom information.
No Unnecessary Data Collection: We do not track, store, or use any personal data beyond these functionalities.
4. Information Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, publish, or share any information collected from you. All data is used solely to provide the intended features of the App.

The App does not integrate with external services that collect or share your personal information.

5. Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect the data processed by the App. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
The App is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

If you believe that we have inadvertently collected data from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted within the App and, if appropriate, communicated to you.

